Advanced Network Analysis: A look into Danish Elite NEtworks

Daniel S. Hain (dsh@business.aau.dk)

Updated October 12, 2020

Danish elites

  • https://github.com/antongrau/eliter

  • https://magtelite.dk/data/

Get the data

# remotes::install_github("antongrau/soc.elite") # Somehow doesnt work

first inspection

All

den17 <- read_csv('https://github.com/SDS-AAU/SDS-master/raw/master/00_data/networks/elite_den17.csv') 

── Column specification ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
cols(
  NAME = col_character(),
  AFFILIATION = col_character(),
  ROLE = col_character(),
  TAGS = col_character(),
  POSITION_ID = col_double(),
  ID = col_double(),
  SECTOR = col_character(),
  TYPE = col_character(),
  DESCRIPTION = col_character(),
  CREATED = col_datetime(format = ""),
  ARCHIVED = col_logical(),
  LAST_CHECKED = col_datetime(format = ""),
  CVR_PERSON = col_double(),
  CVR_AFFILIATION = col_double(),
  PERSON_ID = col_double(),
  AFFILIATION_ID = col_double()
)
den17 %>% head()
den17 %>% count(ROLE, sort = TRUE)
den17 %<>% filter(ROLE %in% c('Member', 'Chairman', 'Vice chairman', 'Chief executive', 'Executive'))
den17 %>% count(TYPE, sort = TRUE)
den17 %<>% drop_na(CVR_AFFILIATION)
den17 %>% count(PERSON_ID, NAME, sort = TRUE)
el <-den17 %>%
  select(PERSON_ID, AFFILIATION_ID) %>%
  left_join(den17 %>% select(PERSON_ID, AFFILIATION_ID), by = "AFFILIATION_ID") 
el %<>% 
  select(-AFFILIATION_ID) %>%
  rename(from = PERSON_ID.x, 
         to = PERSON_ID.y) %>%
  filter(from != to)
el %<>%
  count(from, to, name = 'weight') 
el %>% 
  head()
el %>% arrange(desc(weight)) 
el %>% 
  ggplot(aes(x = weight)) +
  geom_histogram()

create the network

Node names

nodes <- den17 %>% select(PERSON_ID, NAME) %>%
  rename(name = PERSON_ID, label = NAME) %>%
  mutate(name = name %>% as.character()) %>%
  distinct(name, .keep_all = TRUE)
g <- as_tbl_graph(el, directed = FALSE)
g <- g %>% simplify() %>% as_tbl_graph()
g <- g %E>%
  filter(weight > 1) %N>%
  filter(!node_is_isolated())

g <- g %>%
  mutate(community = group_louvain(weights = weight) )
g %N>%
  as_tibble() %>%
  count(community)
g <- g %N>%
  mutate(community = ifelse(community > 6, NA, community))
set.seed(1337)
g %N>% 
  filter(percent_rank(centrality_degree(weights = weight)) > 0.99 ) %>%
  ggraph(layout = 'fr') + 
  geom_edge_link(alpha = 0.25) +
  geom_node_point(aes(size= centrality_degree(), col = community %>% factor())) +
  geom_node_text(aes(label = label, filter = percent_rank(centrality_degree(weights = weight)) > 0.95, alpha = percent_rank(centrality_degree(weights = weight))), repel = TRUE) + 
  theme_graph() +
  theme(legend.position = 'bottom')

g  %N>%
  mutate(cent_drg = centrality_degree(weights = weight)) %>%
  as_tibble() %>%
  arrange(desc(cent_drg)) %>%
  head(50)
g %N>%
  mutate(cent_dgr = centrality_degree(weights = weight)) %>%
  as_tibble() %>%
  group_by(community) %>%
  arrange(desc(cent_dgr)) %>%
  slice(1:10) %>%
  ungroup()
